== Example for an adapter
	
=== Target
		Let's try to implement a real world adapter like a power
			adapter.
			Basically different countries sometimes have
			different electrical
			sockets and in order to make different electrical sockets work
			together with a different plugs the
			use of adapters is necessary.
		
		
