			These classes make clear that only
			`UKPlugConnectors`
			can be
			plugged into a
			`UKElectricalSocket`
			and only
			`GermanPlugConnectors`
			can be
			plugged into
			a
			`GermanElectricalSocket`
			.
		
		
			Fortunately an
			`UKElectricalSocket`
			can also be used with a
			`GermanPlugConnector`
			by using an adapter. This can be archived by wrapping a
			`GermanPlugConnector`
			in a
			`UKPlugConnector`
			.
		

	
